{"tid":1755424,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(重開) 創意來了： 和 你 貼！追撃黨鐵！","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T14:21:03.000Z","uid":73959,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"baadd0f9eb54986e11d8853e79cd49f24527dfcf","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"前言：今日同朋友食飯講開黨鐵惡行，朋友同我propose咗一個方法，去令黨鐵收入減少。聽完我覺得幾得意，不過絕對唔鼓勵大家咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵惡行：<br />\n- 未有發放<span style=\"color: red;\">831太子站CCTV</span><br />\n- 未有交代917東鐵線紅磡站列車出軌炒車事件<br />\n- 變本加厲配合政府宵禁，<span style=\"color: red;\">地鐵站話閂就閂</span><br />\n- 將可正常運作的閘機、售票機用布遮蓋，為求營造車站被嚴重破壞<br />\n- 多次讓<span style=\"color: red;\">警方徴用列車</span><br />\n- 聘請劣質兼職無禮粗暴對待乘客<br />\n- 只<span style=\"color: red;\">加價沒有減價</span>機制<br />\n<br />\n早前有手足以跳閘形式去表達對黨鐵不滿，但其實車資無法有效傷害黨鐵收益。除咗上蓋物業，黨鐵其中一個收入來源係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廣告</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n究竟點樣先可以令廣告商唔再喺車站內登廣告？<br />\n噴污糟佢？打爛廣告牌？唔得。<br />\n你未開工已經被人捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要和平、理性、非暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有&rdquo;和你貼billboard&rdquo;運動<br />\n<br />\nStep 1: 預備標語貼紙<br />\nStep 2: 撕開貼紙<br />\nStep 3: 貼上廣告billboard<br />\nStep 4: 閃人<br />\n<br />\n貼完就咁算呀？當然唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行開行埋如果大家見到 e.g. Dxxtor&rsquo;s Choice廣告上面貼住光復香港 時代革命嘅標語，大家當然要影低佢happy share！<br />\n<br />\n一班人上Facebook問下該公司係咪支持光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一班人又讚下佢哋勇敢發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬，我俾咁多錢係地鐵站度落廣告，但啲stickers阻住我嘅air time，到時黨鐵就無得唔處理，日日要搵人清，仲要加派人手守billboard。<br />\n不過一個地鐵站有咁多個廣告牌，你一邊又要捉人跳閘，我睇吓你守得幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*注意：<br />\n- 因為黨鐵有大量CCTV, 唔建議手足貼自己屋企附近嗰站<br />\n- 先留意附近有冇人mon住, 亦因站內可能有厚多士藍絲，所以過程一定要低調、快！絕對唔可以慢慢搽膠水或者對位。<br />\n- 最好人<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人都貼，好似連儂牆咁撕一貼百</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81279f613b7b2f43b673b84bf2093854284be37f","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"大家千其唔好破壞車站！"},{"pid":"be5bebf9ab995b931706104827a12a6bb17721ba","tid":1755424,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下車手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"bd7b2967a74da94676de0a89aae6f1094c396f90","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"地鐵廣告變連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040ec8129c5ff0d7f66299c57604d97e4c50a24d","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"和理非呢？"},{"pid":"69d496938856233df6701484d552f44e50af843d","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"唔可以唔撘黨鐵的你有嘢做啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87367e3ec6469e9117c4f6096a378874cc2b4dd","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"連儂牆未必個個去睇<br />\n但地鐵廣告冇人可以扮睇唔到啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9576d513c5507ad2cd263b9389613deea3c7596","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f022aba51ce8c3b0d06ba4d39eac964935e61224","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"6c7d9573023db1b91fc453fbc1586158829e29a9","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"1ec5299e51a9debd12f69a51e2e04aef75be2b89","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"8dee8f85910ef5267de18962b9f5b69546660c2e","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"bc6fab57ea6b0c378e69e642740d6872db3601a6","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"4d5d573058d7dbfbe7f32eae245a84ed9b62c90b","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"14ec492b8e3bb27700722b52aace336925fca13d","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:58.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"c72ba4ff4cf6f8ec347982c64b18bb889490038d","tid":1755424,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f419b599cd8c1298fea4e767415b2d6b4b11d75","tid":1755424,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:55:45.000Z","msg":"黨鐵又側側膊 賺到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494f76d21008bf10794fed49ba2d1bdc13585490","tid":1755424,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:56: